author: gtully
msg: resolve https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/AMQ-2283. In suppressing asyncColos I found the need to suppress brodcast of query parameters by the multicast discovery agent as server side and client side options are not compatible. Added support to the DiscoveryTransport to apply query parameters to each uri that it discovers.
